{"tid":949576,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中遠海能（1138）董事總經理賈利賓於台灣墮樓身亡","createTime":"2018-12-21T01:59:48.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-21T02:04:01.000Z","uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d1d2214b19a6f3f7b10a41f71e1c487d0bc2d276","tid":949576,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-21T01:59:48.000Z","msg":"香港上市公司中遠海能（1138）董事總經理賈利賓，今日凌晨2時許在台北市的五星級王朝大酒店，留下9頁遺書後，從15樓開窗跳樓輕生，酒店人員發現後報警，但賈送院搶救後傷重不治。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，賈利賓（39歲）本月18日入境台灣，警員接報後到場發現他右手腕骨折，雙腳大腿骨折，已無生命迹象，將他送往馬偕醫院急救後宣告不治。<br />\n<br />\n酒店人員向警方表示，賈利賓昨晚獨自入住酒店時，服務人員察覺他似乎精神有異狀，他入住後在房間留下長達9頁的遺書，多數是提到家人及朋友，最後一頁寫下「FAREWELL」與親友們告別。<br />\n<br />\n廣告<br />\n<br />\n台灣《蘋果日報》<br />\n<br />\n24小時求助熱線：<br />\n珍愛生命長者熱線:2382 0881<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會熱線:2389 2222<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言):2896 0000<br />\n生命熱線:2382 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園熱線:18281<br />\n社會福利署熱線:2343 2255<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181221/59053993?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F59053993%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&d=DcGHbNw%2B4eT%2BJYIid6iYFlKzBYqMCiHg3GgvTcrvEuQ%3D&h=ee38d02c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181221%2F59053993%3Fitm_campaign%3Dhkad_internal_link%26itm_medium%3Dinternal%26itm_source%3Dhkad_mweb%26itm_content%3Dinternal_link_1&h=4ab85e6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20181221/59053993?itm_campaign=hkad_internal_link&amp;itm_medium=internal&amp;itm_source=hkad_mweb&amp;itm_content=internal_link_1</a>"},{"pid":"cf130fee937c8c187e48b92b6872f5371d303bca","tid":949576,"uid":139940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedB